INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','product','0','12','12','und','0','<p>Rarely does a home so easily capture the imagination as this storybook c1908 family retreat, where heritage character and contemporary finesse converge against a mesmeric water backdrop. ''Heathcote'' is surrounded by gorgeous gardens on an idyllic street-to-shore parcel in Hunters Hill''s most coveted street.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Original timber and marble finishes highlight period elegance<br />\r\n	- Astute architectural redesign has ensured modern liveability<br />\r\n	- Grand lounge/dining rooms beneath beautiful ornate ceilings<br />\r\n	- Selection of bespoke family zones open to picturesque grounds<br />\r\n	- Classic verandah, swimming pool and spa embrace river views<br />\r\n	- Idyllic waterside lawns, private beach, sandstone boathouse<br />\r\n	- Ilve appointed chefs'' kitchen set around castile marble island<br />\r\n	- Indulgent master retreat with dressing room and full ensuite<br />\r\n	- Private children''s wing, versatile lower level includes cellar<br />\r\n	- Home security/audio systems, internal lift from dual garage<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	KEY DETAILS:<br />\r\n	Council rates: $5,200pa<br />\r\n	Water rates: $688pa</p>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','custom_page','0','13','13','und','0','  <script data-cfasync="false" type="text/javascript" src="../custom code/form-submission-handler.js"></script>\r\n  <style>\r\n    label, input, textarea, button {\r\n      display: block;\r\n      width: 40%;\r\n    }\r\n  </style>\r\n  \r\n\r\n  <h2 id="header">Contact the company through this form</h2>\r\n\r\n  <form class="gform" method="POST" data-email="dqcuong93@gmail.com" id="email_form" action="https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbx9Me2a9uZVSrfLuSt-bWqvxzYGw6J1hT3303sqCwW4KevA5m8/exec">\r\n    <label>Name</label>\r\n    <input name="name" type="text" placeholder="Type your name here" autocomplete="on">\r\n    <label>Email</label>\r\n    <input id="email" name="email" 